{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775810639874,"sessionID":"ses_28972ce95ffeGkZSE6XM6ARimn","part":{"id":"prt_d768ff473001urs3xeueNXp4OQ","messageID":"msg_d768fb613001kJi05BUCD5zfoT","sessionID":"ses_28972ce95ffeGkZSE6XM6ARimn","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_399483b8b6014a2f9dc31fa6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 任务清单\n2: \n3: > **Stage**: ST-3 (Design Complete)\n4: > **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n5: > **Language**: Go\n6: > **Size**: S\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## T-001: 创建 codeinterpreter_types.go — 共享类型定义\n11: \n12: - [ ] T-001.01 定义 `type ProtocolType string`\n13: - [ ] T-001.02 定义常量 `ProtocolTypeHTTP ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"` 和 `ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"`\n14: - [ ] T-001.03 定义 `type AuthModeType string`\n15: - [ ] T-001.04 定义常量 `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"` 和 `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n16: - [ ] T-001.05 定义 `type TargetPort struct`，字段：`PathPrefix string`、`Name string`、`Port uint32`、`Protocol ProtocolType`\n17: - [ ] T-001.06 所有字段使用正确的 JSON tag（camelCase: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, `protocol`）\n18: \n19: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`；`AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ## T-002: 创建 CodeInterpreter 根类型\n24: \n25: - [ ] T-002.01 定义 `type CodeInterpreter struct`，嵌入 `metav1.TypeMeta` 和 `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n26: - [ ] T-002.02 字段 `Spec CodeInterpreterSpec`（JSON tag: `spec`）\n27: - [ ] T-002.03 字段 `Status CodeInterpreterStatus`（JSON tag: `status,omitempty`）\n28: - [ ] T-002.04 添加标记 `+genclient`\n29: - [ ] T-002.05 添加标记 `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n30: - [ ] T-002.06 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n31: - [ ] T